HDO BOX - Movies app for Android, iOS, and TV.
Best Application for watching movies on any device.

When updating: you need to update from this GitHub, not from the app.. 

Download:
----

AD-Free on this github..

Ad-free features: no ads!, faster load times, no waiting, free content for all!

Installation: If you have HDO Box already on the device, remove it, then install this one, and the mod show be in place and work.. 

We recommend to use a DNS (not the same exactly to a VPN) to spead up servers load time, like personaldnsfilter from the play store or fdroid.. (will also help block ads)

